resources.string: ଯଦି ଯାଞ୍ଚ କରାଯାଏ, ତେବେ ପୋଷ୍ଟଟି ଆପଣଙ୍କ ବ୍ଲଗରେ ତାଲିକାଭୁକ୍ତ ହେବ। ଯଦି ନୁହେଁ, ତେବେ ଏହା ଆପଣଙ୍କ ଡ୍ରାଫ୍ଟ ପୋଷ୍ଟଗୁଡ଼ିକରେ ବ୍ୟକ୍ତିଗତ ରହିବ

string.name: imageAlt
string.comment:
imageAlt
You can add alternative text (or 'alt text') to describe an image in words, for the benefit of partially sighted or blind users.

string.name: imageCredit
string.comment:
imageCredit
A field in case the image is not yours, so you can note who took the photo for example or other forms of copyright.
